latestIgtvVideos.caption:
A piece of furniture is what it takes 
to make your room feel new all of a sudden. 
With the new year, it’s time to make the house look fresh by adding a pinch of newness and what better way to do that other than bringing exotic and authentic handcrafted pieces of furniture at your doorstep. This is your sign to elevate the “shobha” of your house with a TWIST. It’s time to welcome 2022 with Wooden Twist! @woodentwist
Put life into your rooms with Wooden Twist’s range of wooden handicrafts, home decor, and furniture.

The piece I have with me here is their Wooden Laptop table. 
This table is lightweight but sturdy, super compact, has holders for all my devices & is broad enough so I can work on my laptop & write in my notebook at the same time.

Your gateway to bringing a twist is a click away. Hit the link in my bio and unlock the doors to making new memories with Wooden Twist.

"No one has ever become poor by giving." - Anne Frank

Got an invite from @the_msg_foundation to be a part of their Eid-al-Adha celebrations & it was definitely one of the best times for me.

The Madad Sahyog Guidance foundation is working to uplift the underprivileged sections of the society - by providing aid in areas of healthcare, education & community services. The dedicated volunteers at this organization are investing all their time & efforts in helping to build a better life for others. What they need from us is to provide financial assistance to this organization, so they could expand their working & make an even bigger impact. So if you are able to, please do donate generously to this cause.

You can connect with them through DM on @the_msg_foundation or on their WhatsApp number +91-7985449379. For more details, please check www.themsgfoundation.org
